42:22.839 --> 42:23.738
<i>Don't be so silly.</i>

42:23.739 --> 42:24.772
Dan: <i> Well, there's nobody around.</i>

42:24.839 --> 42:25.792
<i>Oh, but you never can tell when there's</i>

42:25.817 --> 42:26.696
- <i>someone around.
- Then I'll come in.</i>

42:26.724 --> 42:28.307
<i>Oh, no, Dan, I wouldn't come in</i>
<i>if I were you.</i>

42:28.342 --> 42:30.843
<i>- Really, we're going to be awfully late.
- Well, don't be bashful, Lucy.</i>

42:30.895 --> 42:32.728
<i>Well, I'm not bashful, but</i>
<i>I've never kissed you before,</i>

42:32.763 --> 42:34.730
<i>and I don't think</i>
<i>this is exactly the place.</i>

42:34.765 --> 42:36.682
<i>Gosh, if you knew how crazy I am about you,</i>

42:36.734 --> 42:39.834
<i>you wouldn't hesitate...</i>
<i>I can't sleep nights.</i>

42:40.034 --> 42:41.734
<i>Oh, why don't you take some hot milk?</i>

42:41.786 --> 42:43.569
<i>I guess I must be in love,</i>
<i>'cause it started right...</i>

42:43.585 --> 42:46.086
[Television mutes]

