[Knocking on door]

43:07.309 --> 43:09.359
[Knocking continues]

43:09.394 --> 43:11.895
[Door hinges creak]

43:18.120 --> 43:20.220
Long way from home, aren't you?

43:20.255 --> 43:22.589
You and me both.

